---
title: Creamy Roasted Veggie & Corn Soup with Extra Cheddar Cheese & Parsley
description: A bowl of hearty, comforting soup is easily our favourite way to warm up when the weather cools down! This one is packed full of goodness, with an array of roasted veggies and pops of sweetcorn in a creamy broth. A sprinkle of Cheddar at the end adds the perfect amount of richness and cheesy deliciousness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66299f2b4973a916e18c1120-47554209.jpeg
